etes\", \"from\": 241, \"to\": 249}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic and Paralympic Village\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: REUTERS PublishedFeb 29, 2024, 01:09 PM UpdatedFeb 29, 2024, 11:49 PM PARIS-The athletes' village for the Paris Olympics, which was inaugurated on Feb 29, contains a host of innovations intended to make it a model of low-carbon construction.\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PHOTO\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 347}, {\"ngram\": \"REUTERS PublishedFeb\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 369}, {\"ngram\": \"PM\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 418}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 469}, {\"ngram\": \"Feb\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 499}, {\"ngram\": \"a host\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 519}, {\"ngram\": \"innovations\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 534}, {\"ngram\": \"low-carbon construction\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Faced with concerns about the vast emissions caused by the Games - from the construction work, the air miles and catering - Paris 2024 organisers set out to make the village as environmentally friendly as possible.\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 809, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2804883669747117e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 614}, {\"ngram\": \"the vast emissions\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 659}, {\"ngram\": \"the construction work\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 688}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With its roughly 40 different blocks, it was intended to be a \\\"coherent model of the best things we can do at the start of the 21st century, even a bit ahead of time\\\", said the head of the Paris Olympics infrastructure group, Nicolas Ferrand.\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 1053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1000, \"end\": 1014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its roughly 40 different blocks\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 847}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"coherent model\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"the best things\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 907}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 930}, {\"ngram\": \"the 21st century\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"the head\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"Nicolas Ferrand\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2,800 housing units will generate around half of the carbon emissions of equivalents that are built with regular construction techniques when energy savings over their lifetimes are taken into account, said the Paris Games infrastructure body Solideo.\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2,800 housing units\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"half\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\": \"the carbon emissions\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1128}, {\"ngram\": \"equivalents\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1143}, {\"ngram\": \"regular construction techniques\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"energy savings\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"their lifetimes\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"account\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1259}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games infrastructure body Solideo\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After they have been used by Olympians and Paralympians from July 26 to Sept 8, the apartments will be converted into homes, with at least a third destined for public housing.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1350}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympians\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"Sept\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1388}, {\"ngram\": \"the apartments\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"homes\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1435}, {\"ngram\": \"public housing\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are some of their features.\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1521, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their features\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1520}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers are proud of offering an Olympic village that they say does not require air-conditioning to keep residents cool, with temperatures inside set to be at least 6 deg C lower than outside in summer.\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1728, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organisers\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1533}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic village\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"air-conditioning\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1622}, {\"ngram\": \"residents\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"temperatures\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1664}, {\"ngram\": \"at least 6 deg C\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1698}, {\"ngram\": \"summer\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As well as high-performance insulation and sun shades, the secret is reversible underfloor plumbing linked to a local geothermal power plant.\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1871, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"high-performance insulation\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"sun\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"the secret\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1795}, {\"ngram\": \"reversible underfloor plumbing\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1829}, {\"ngram\": \"a local geothermal power plant\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It draws cool water from beneath the surface during the summer and heat from far underground in the winter.\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1979, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cool water\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1891}, {\"ngram\": \"the surface\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1916}, {\"ngram\": \"the summer\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 1934}, {\"ngram\": \"heat\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1943}, {\"ngram\": \"the winter\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The renewable system helps dramatically reduce operational costs and the carbon footprint of the buildings.\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2088, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The renewable system\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2001}, {\"ngram\": \"operational costs\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2045}, {\"ngram\": \"the carbon footprint\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2070}, {\"ngram\": \"the buildings\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2087}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Real estate companies had to agree to build the flats while generating 30 per cent less emissions per square metre than a traditional building under the terms of their contracts, according to Georgina Grenon, head of sustainability for the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2342, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2282, \"end\": 2290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgina_River\", \"score\": 0.999999524275267, \"rank\": 4.751765548298621e-07, \"text\": \"Georgina\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgina_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgina_River\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Real estate companies\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"the flats\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"30 per cent less emissions\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2187}, {\"ngram\": \"square metre\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2204}, {\"ngram\": \"a traditional building\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2232}, {\"ngram\": \"the terms\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2248}, {\"ngram\": \"their contracts\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2267}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2303}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainability\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2321}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That brought up new construction techniques,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new construction techniques\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2,800 apartments will generate around half of the carbon emissions of equivalents that are built with regular construction techniques.\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2540, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2,800 apartments\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2422}, {\"ngram\": \"half\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2448}, {\"ngram\": \"the carbon emissions\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2472}, {\"ngram\": \"equivalents\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2487}, {\"ngram\": \"regular construction techniques\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: REUTERS In many cases, the builders swopped carbon-intensive concrete for wood, resulting in many of the structures using the natural material for their core support, as well as facades and floors.\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2747, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PHOTO\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2547}, {\"ngram\": \"REUTERS\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2556}, {\"ngram\": \"many cases\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2570}, {\"ngram\": \"the builders\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2584}, {\"ngram\": \"carbon-intensive concrete\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2618}, {\"ngram\": \"wood\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2627}, {\"ngram\": \"the structures\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2664}, {\"ngram\": \"the natural material\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"their core support\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2714}, {\"ngram\": \"facades\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2734}, {\"ngram\": \"floors\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Low-carbon concrete - which uses less energy-intensive materials and processes to make the bonding agent - was widely used across the site.\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Low-carbon concrete\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2768}, {\"ngram\": \"less energy-intensive materials\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2813}, {\"ngram\": \"processes\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2827}, {\"ngram\": \"the bonding agent\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2853}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We chose materials not for their technical, economic or architectural qualities, but for their carbon footprint,\\\" said Julie Bosch, project director for real estate group Vinci Immobilier, which built part of the village.\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 3112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3016, \"end\": 3021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Bosch_GmbH\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.650094416457455e-13, \"text\": \"Bosch\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Bosch_GmbH\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Bosch_GmbH\"}, {\"begin\": 3062, \"end\": 3078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinci_SA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinci Immobilier\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinci_SA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinci_SA\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"materials\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2909}, {\"ngram\": \"their technical, economic or architectural qualities\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2970}, {\"ngram\": \"their carbon footprint\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 3002}, {\"ngram\": \"project director\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3039}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3096}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The village has large gardens that will account for 40 per cent of total land space and include 9,000 trees and shrubs once the area has been fully developed after the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The village\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3125}, {\"ngram\": \"large gardens\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3143}, {\"ngram\": \"40 per cent\", \"from\": 3166, \"to\": 3177}, {\"ngram\": \"total land space\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3197}, {\"ngram\": \"9,000 trees\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3221}, {\"ngram\": \"shrubs\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3232}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3246}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3278, \"to\": 3290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a very high ratio, and with our system of recycling water, it will enable areas for relaxation and cooling off,\\\" said Charles Richard-Molard, deputy director in charge of public spaces at Solideo.\", \"from\": 3293, \"to\": 3495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3417, \"end\": 3424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_II_of_England\", \"score\": 0.7991156897761881, \"rank\": 0.2512588830067716, \"text\": \"Charles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_II_of_England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_II_of_England\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very high ratio\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3316}, {\"ngram\": \"our system\", \"from\": 3327, \"to\": 3337}, {\"ngram\": \"recycling water\", \"from\": 3341, \"to\": 3356}, {\"ngram\": \"areas\", \"from\": 3373, \"to\": 3378}, {\"ngram\": \"relaxation\", \"from\": 3383, \"to\": 3393}, {\"ngram\": \"deputy director\", \"from\": 3441, \"to\": 3456}, {\"ngram\": \"charge\", \"from\": 3460, \"to\": 3466}, {\"ngram\": \"public spaces\", \"from\": 3470, \"to\": 3483}, {\"ngra