\", \"from\": 3714, \"to\": 3749}, {\"ngram\": \"waste water\", \"from\": 3780, \"to\": 3791}, {\"ngram\": \"the gardens\", \"from\": 3818, \"to\": 3829}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One experimental building will use purified rainwater for its toilets, which are designed to separate out urine and faeces which can then be converted into fertilisers.\", \"from\": 3833, \"to\": 4001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One experimental building\", \"from\": 3833, \"to\": 3858}, {\"ngram\": \"purified rainwater\", \"from\": 3868, \"to\": 3886}, {\"ngram\": \"its toilets\", \"from\": 3891, \"to\": 3902}, {\"ngram\": \"urine\", \"from\": 3939, \"to\": 3944}, {\"ngram\": \"faeces\", \"from\": 3949, \"to\": 3955}, {\"ngram\": \"fertilisers\", \"from\": 3989, \"to\": 4000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of the roughly 300,000 household items destined for the Olympic village, all are set for a second life afterwards.\", \"from\": 4003, \"to\": 4117, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the roughly 300,000 household items\", \"from\": 4006, \"to\": 4041}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic village\", \"from\": 4055, \"to\": 4074}, {\"ngram\": \"a second life\", \"from\": 4092, \"to\": 4105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We signed with suppliers only if they were able to show that they would be able to recycle or re-use,\\\" said Julia Watson, deputy director for the village works at Solideo.\", \"from\": 4119, \"to\": 4291, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4228, \"end\": 4240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_Watson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Julia Watson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_Watson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_Watson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"suppliers\", \"from\": 4135, \"to\": 4144}, {\"ngram\": \"use\", \"from\": 4217, \"to\": 4220}, {\"ngram\": \"deputy director\", \"from\": 4242, \"to\": 4257}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 4262, \"to\": 4273}, {\"ngram\": \"Solideo\", \"from\": 4283, \"to\": 4290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bed bases will be made of reinforced cardboard and the mattresses are being manufactured from recycled fishing nets - the same system as at the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 4293, \"to\": 4456, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The bed bases\", \"from\": 4293, \"to\": 4306}, {\"ngram\": \"reinforced cardboard\", \"from\": 4323, \"to\": 4343}, {\"ngram\": \"the mattresses\", \"from\": 4348, \"to\": 4362}, {\"ngram\": \"recycled fishing nets\", \"from\": 4391, \"to\": 4412}, {\"ngram\": \"the same system\", \"from\": 4415, \"to\": 4430}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 4437, \"to\": 4455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Much of the wooden street furniture is from reclaimed wood, while some of the street lighting has been made from recycled steel piping.AFP Olympics 2024 Environmental issues Recycling E-paper Newsletters Podcasts RSS Feed About Us Terms & Conditions Personal Data Protection Notice Need help?\", \"from\": 4458, \"to\": 4765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4682, \"end\": 4690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RSS Feed\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wooden street furniture\", \"from\": 4466, \"to\": 4493}, {\"ngram\": \"reclaimed wood\", \"from\": 4502, \"to\": 4516}, {\"ngram\": \"the street lighting\", \"from\": 4532, \"to\": 4551}, {\"ngram\": \"recycled steel piping\", \"from\": 4571, \"to\": 4592}, {\"ngram\": \"E-paper Newsletters Podcasts\", \"from\": 4642, \"to\": 4670}, {\"ngram\": \"Conditions Personal Data Protection Notice\", \"from\": 4697, \"to\": 4739}, {\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 4745, \"to\": 4749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reach us here.\", \"from\": 4766, \"to\": 4780, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4772, \"to\": 4774}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertise with us\", \"from\": 4782, \"to\": 4799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Advertise\", \"from\": 4782, \"to\": 4791}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4797, \"to\": 4799}]}]}"